reviewText: This is one of Slim and the Supremes best Concert ever. He gives a great performance. You will really enjoy it. It is Scotty's last performance. If you ever was a Slim and the Supreme Angel fan this video is a must see.

Death and The Beautiful Lady is classic. All fans of the Supreme Angels should have it. This is also the last performance of Scotty. He was a member of the Supreme Angels from the beginning. Great concert.
